description.narrative: The Project Development Objective is to help in the revitalization of private sector activities in the four major urban cities of Kabul, Mazar-e-Sharif, Jalalabad and Herat through provision of business development technical assistance to support private firms initiatives to gain market knowledge, improve product quality and processing technologies, and increase their presence in th domestic and export markets.
